# HardwareSwapNotifier
Receive a text or email when an item is posted on Reddit.com/r/HardwareSwap

Compile with external jar, mail.jar

javac -cp ".:mail.jar" Main.java 

**Version 1.1**

It is now much easier to use without the use of gathering external links and using email addresses. Everything can now be done within the program!

  Some notable new features.

  * No longer need to add a keyword.

  * No longer need to add an email address.

  * Manually change check interval.

  * Remove post when found.

  * Remove Phone Numbers/Items within the program

  * Save Current

  * Help Menu
